<svg viewBox="0 0 220 150" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><line x1="20" y1="10" x2="20" y2="130" stroke="#1f2937" stroke-width="1.5"/><line x1="20" y1="130" x2="210" y2="130" stroke="#1f2937" stroke-width="1.5"/><rect x="35" y="60" width="30" height="70" fill="#f97316" stroke="#1f2937" stroke-width="1.5"/><rect x="80" y="80" width="30" height="50" fill="#3b82f6" stroke="#1f2937" stroke-width="1.5"/><rect x="125" y="100" width="30" height="30" fill="#10b981" stroke="#1f2937" stroke-width="1.5"/><rect x="170" y="120" width="30" height="10" fill="#eab308" stroke="#1f2937" stroke-width="1.5"/><text x="50" y="55" font-size="13" text-anchor="middle" fill="#1f2937">7</text><text x="95" y="75" font-size="13" text-anchor="middle" fill="#1f2937">5</text><text x="140" y="95" font-size="13" text-anchor="middle" fill="#1f2937">3</text><text x="185" y="115" font-size="13" text-anchor="middle" fill="#1f2937">1</text><text x="50" y="145" font-size="13" text-anchor="middle" fill="#1f2937">أ</text><text x="95" y="145" font-size="13" text-anchor="middle" fill="#1f2937">ب</text><text x="140" y="145" font-size="13" text-anchor="middle" fill="#1f2937">ج</text><text x="185" y="145" font-size="13" text-anchor="middle" fill="#1f2937">د</text></svg>', '[{"id":"a","text":"تفّاح"},{"id":"b","text":"موز"},{"id":"c","text":"برتقال"},{"id":"d","text":"عنب"}]'::jsonb, 'd', 'أقصرُ عمودٍ في الرسم هو العمودُ د (عنب) بارتفاعٍ يمثّل التواتر 1، وهو أصغرُ التواترات الأربعة (7؛ 5؛ 3؛ 1)، فالعنبُ هو الفاكهةُ الأقلُّ اختيارًا.', 4, 'mcq', NULL, NULL)
